<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/6257942-drea-kreth">Drea Kreth</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Open the front cover towards the left if you are reading a book written in English. Continue turning pages until you come to a page that has words on <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">â€¦more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Open the front cover towards the left if you are reading a book written in English. Continue turning pages until you come to a page that has words on it. Begin to read the words. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
